            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>Il <rs key="#Other_clerics">chierico</rs>
                        <persName key="#Other_clerics"><name ref="Gherardus"
                            >Gherardo</name></persName> figlio <rs key="#Clerical_concubinage">della
                                <persName key="#Clerical_concubinage">fu <name ref="Immilga"
                                    >Imilga</name></persName></rs>, avendo ricevuto dal <rs
                            key="#Priests">prete</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Iohannes">Giovanni</name></persName>
                        figlio <rs key="#Clerical_concubinage">di <persName
                                key="#Clerical_concubinage"><name ref="Liutia"
                                >Liuzia</name></persName></rs>, <rs key="#Meritum/launechild"
                            >meritum argentum</rs> pro 82 soldi, promette di non contestare
                        duodecimam portionem della <rs key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> dei <orgName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3106">Santi Salvatore e
                            Andrea</orgName> posta in loco et finibus <placeName ref="#places/3103"
                            >Buslangno</placeName> con tutte le sue dipendenze poste nello stesso
                        luogo et per loca et funda nocupante <placeName ref="#places/3104">Casa
                            Lei</placeName>
                        <placeName ref="#places/3104">Aquavivula</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Common_land"><placeName key="#Common_land" ref="#places/3104"
                                >Beneficio Comunallia</placeName></rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/3104">Guindalfo</placeName> et in <placeName
                            ref="#places/3104">Aldio</placeName> et in <placeName ref="#places/3104"
                            >Plaie que vocatur Vingnaldoresi</placeName> et in loco ubi dicitur
                            <placeName ref="#places/3104">Terra della Russa</placeName> et in eorum
                        finibus ed omnibus casis et terris seo rebus quas abeo fini <rs
                            key="#Baptismal_churches">ecclesia et plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Baptismal_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3107"><placeName
                                ref="#places/3106">Sancti Stefani</placeName></orgName> usque ad <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/287">Sancti
                            Angeli</orgName> que dicitur in <placeName ref="#places/294"
                            >Cornuta</placeName> et fini <placeName ref="#places/3105">Ponte que
                            dicitur Sancti Petri</placeName> de <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio Serclo</rs>
                        usque ad locum que dicitur <placeName>Hischia Donbelli</placeName> et in
                        eorum finibus, quas tibi odie per <rs key="#Venditio">cartula</rs> scripta
                        ex manibus del <rs key="#Notary">notaio imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Rainerius"
                            >Ranieri</name></persName> ex comperatione obveni ad me ipso. Nel caso
                        non rispetti le suddette condizioni promette con i suoi eredi di versare al
                        prete e ai suoi eredi una pena di 10 libbre dâ€™argento. Chiede al <rs
                            key="#Writer #Notary">notaio imperiale</rs> Ranieri la stesura della
                        cartula. Actum <placeName ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>. <rs
                            key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori: <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Morandus">Morando</name></persName> di <persName><name
                                ref="Paganus">Pagano</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Signorectus">Signoretto</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Sassus">Sasso</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Bernardus">Bernardo</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ingefredus">Inghifridi</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Heinricus">Enrico</name></persName>.</ab>
                        </div>
